parameters:
General Atu: Well, let's talk about the mission this time.
Originally, it was nothing more than a goblin hunt.

General Atu: However, I received eyewitness reports at the
timing when the goblins suddenly became active.

General Atu: A mythical monster, a symbol of calamity... a
dragon!

General Atu: I heard about your mission from Agonia. There
might be a dragon behind the goblin's sudden activity.
Clea: Thank you for allowing me to participate here...!

General Atu: Well, first of all, I want you to carry out the
goblin extermination in the Sazani Grasslands.

General Atu: Once you've taken care of most of it, please
come back. I'm counting on you.

General Atu: There's something off about the goblins'
movements... I don't know the reason though.

General Atu: I'm glad you came. Please tell me what happened
in the Sazani Grasslands!

General Atu: I see, so they assessed the situation and
fled... Hm, I don't recall ever witnessing such behavior
myself.
General Atu: Please let me hear Goblin Slayer's opinion.

One-Armed Opro: The one leading the goblins is an orc... In
front of orcs, goblins become nothing more than a makeshift
unit.

One-Armed Opro: The one leading the goblins is an ogre...
When there's an ogre present, the goblins become a highly
trained unit.
Clea: Are you saying that there is an ogre somewhere?

One-Armed Opro: That's right... If there's something we
can't understand, it's the fact that not only ogres, but
even orcs haven't appeared.

One-Armed Opro: There might be some issue with the
disorganized ogre leading them.

General Atu: If we haven't fought against ogres yet, this is
a rare opportunity if we happen to encounter them!

General Atu: Inform everyone! We will offer a reward to
anyone who finds the ogre!
Imperial Soldier: Yes, I will relay the message to everyone!

General Atu: If you happen to find the ogre, please report
it to me so that I can issue a request for its elimination!
Clea: Is it okay if we defeat it?

General Atu: Hahaha, Agonia has recruited some excellent
warriors! Of course, I don't mind. When that time comes, I
will give an additional reward!

One-Armed Opro: The ogre has been my prey for a long time...
Well then, let me handle it as I please.

General Atu: You guys can go too! Now, I have to prepare for
the battle against the ogre.

General Atu: I am also searching for ogres, not just you
all. Of course, I am not an exception... my arm is hurting.
Clea: I have defeated the ogre.

Imperial Soldier: May I see some evidence? There have been
several false reports of defeating ogres.

Clea: Evidence... I don't have any in particular, but the
place where I defeated it is a cave called Yuan's Maw.
Imperial Soldier: I can't believe it without any proof.
General Atu: Clea, look into my eyes.

General Atu: I understand, I will believe you! Well done for
successfully subduing the ogre.

General Atu: There's no need to say something so tasteless.
Your demeanor is completely different from before you came
here.

General Atu: It's the eyes of someone who has been on the
front lines, who has passed through the brink of death.

Clea: It was an incredibly formidable enemy. If I didn't
have my comrades, there's no way I could have won against
it.

General Atu: Well, the reward alone is not enough... I've
got it!

General Atu: Let's give you the right to participate in the
Pizma Arena! Warriors as skilled as you will compete in
mind, technique, and body.

General Atu: You may gain a lot by participating in the
tournament, but haha, please don't do anything that would
tarnish my reputation.

General Atu: I am pleased with your work! If there is
another opportunity, I will make a request through the
Adventurer's Guild.
Clea: Yes. Thank you very much!

General Atu: Well then, I'll leave the aftermath to you
guys. I'll go report to the old hag at the royal palace, so
I'm counting on you!

General Atu: That's right, the arena is located in the
martial arts city of Jinami in Fotizona. It would be good
for you to go and check it out.

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Fotizona Region/Martial Arts
City Jinami\c[0]
実績 ピズマ闘技場の挑戦者
One-armed Opro: 'To meet you all here...'

Imperial Soldier: The movements of the goblins are beyond
strange.

Imperial Soldier: Since then, there haven't been any more
damages caused by goblins. Thank you all for your help.
